EsxHostAdvSettings.Mem.ShareForceSalting.label="份额 force salting"
EsxHostAdvSettings.Mem.ShareForceSalting.summary="P份额 salting lets you 限制 the transparent page sharing only 介于 a 设置 of VMs. P份额 salting is controlled by the VMX sched.mem.p份额.salt option. The P份额 salting option has three 状态s: 0 - no salting or isolation 介于 VMs; 1 - VMs that have the sched.mem.p份额.salt option 设置 are able to 份额 内存 with VMs 使用 same salt; 2 - VMs that do not have the sched.mem.p份额.salt option 设置 cannot 份额 内存 with any other VM, page sharing is possible only insIDE the VM. If the  sched.mem.p份额.salt is present but empty, the VM gets its own unique salt."
