EsxHostAdvSettings.Syslog.global.logDir.label="Sys日志.global.日志Dir"
EsxHostAdvSettings.Syslog.global.logDir.summary="数据存储 path 的 directory to output 日志 to. Example: [数据存储名称]/日志dir"
EsxHostAdvSettings.Syslog.global.logDirUnique.label="Sys日志.global.日志DirUnique"
EsxHostAdvSettings.Syslog.global.logDirUnique.summary="启用 placing 日志 files in a unique subdirectory of 日志dir, 基于 主机名称."
EsxHostAdvSettings.Syslog.global.logFilters.label="Sys日志.global.日志Filters"
EsxHostAdvSettings.Syslog.global.logFilters.summary="Double vertical bar (||) separated list of 日志 filters. The 格式 of a 日志 filter is: num日志 | IDEnt | 日志Regexp. 'num日志s' 设置s the maximum number of 日志 entries 的 specified 日志 messages. After reaching this number, the specified 日志 messages are filtered 和 ignored. 'IDEnt' specifies one or more system components to 应用 the filter 到 日志 messages that these components 生成. '日志Regexp' specifies a case-sensitive phrase with Python regular expression syntax to filter the 日志 messages by their content."
EsxHostAdvSettings.Syslog.global.logFiltersEnable.label="Sys日志.global.日志Filters启用"
EsxHostAdvSettings.Syslog.global.logFiltersEnable.summary="启用 the use of 日志 filters."
EsxHostAdvSettings.Syslog.global.logHost.label="Sys日志.global.日志主机"
EsxHostAdvSettings.Syslog.global.logHost.summary="Comma (,) separated list of remote 主机s to 发送 messages to. 格式 is: proto://主机名称|ipv4|'['ipv6']'[:端口][?格式ter=值[&framing=值]]. Protocol must be one of (tcp|udp|ssl). If a 端口 不 provIDEd, ssl 和 tcp will use 1514; udp will use 514. 格式ter must be one of (RFC_3164|RFC_5424). Framing must be one of (octet_计数ing|non_transparent). The default 格式ter is RFC 3164; the default framing is non_transparent."
EsxHostAdvSettings.Syslog.global.logLevel.label="Sys日志.global.日志Level"
EsxHostAdvSettings.Syslog.global.logLevel.summary="日志 filtering level. This should only be 更改 when troubleshooting an issue 使用 sys日志 守护进程. 值s may be '调试' (most detailed level), 'info' (default detail level), '警告' (only 警告s or 错误), or '错误' (only 错误)."
EsxHostAdvSettings.Syslog.global.msgQueueDropMark.label="Sys日志.global.msg已排队ropMark"
EsxHostAdvSettings.Syslog.global.msgQueueDropMark.summary="message queue drop mark (as a 百分比)."
