EsxHostAdvSettings.USB.devsShared.summary="启用 sharing (aka non-exclusive claiming) of USB 设备s with specified vendor 和 model IDs.  0x0 is a wild card model which matches all models 从 specified vendor.  The string must contain colon de限制ed numeric fields, respectively the vendor_ID 和 product ID.  If the latter is omitted 从 last pair it is assumed to be 0x0."
EsxHostAdvSettings.USB.quirks.label="USB.quirks"
EsxHostAdvSettings.USB.quirks.summary="添加itional USB 设备 quirks to be 添加 到 vmkUSB native 驱动程序 default quirks.  设备 quirks are software workarounds for hardware errata.  String 格式 is <vID>:<pID>:<low rev>:<high rev>:<quirk 名称>, with colon de限制ed fields.  vID 和 pID are the \"USB ID\" numbers 的 USB 设备 vendor 和 product, respectively (和 例如, 0x0e0f for vendor VMware), 和 low 和 high rev are the revisions (inclusive) 介于 which to 应用 the quirk (例如, 0 和 0xffff).  Quirk 名称 is a string constant starting with UQ_.  Contact VMware sup端口 for a full list of 有效 quirk 名称s."
